{"tid":230751,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"成日有人話想整個網站創業","createTime":"2017-05-05T14:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T19:37:24.000Z","uid":75893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b298bd4d5a8aa130b59654907a66c2100b7804ac","tid":230751,"uid":75893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:50:47.000Z","msg":"通常會話自己有個idea, 但唔識整web<br />\n想搵d IT人&quot;幫&quot;手<br />\n<br />\n你話如果web programmer + graphic designer + 文科仔寫content<br />\n都叫做合作<br />\n但整d唔係content-oriented (唔洗搵人長期出文),<br />\n又冇讀design既幫手畫圖(要隻it狗自己搵圖)<br />\n得班BBA仔吹話想要d咩function<br />\n<br />\n咁都幫既一定係白痴仔<br />\n佢地講到明唔識 大多數之後都唔會學<br />\n於是成個創業大計就得條IT佬自己搞<br />\n但成果就成班人一齊分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a140f78e2fef2539d42121d51f51eea58b6f992","tid":230751,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:59:53.000Z","msg":"叫個班人裝 linux"},{"pid":"bf546ef53097a4b550ef3357f99239bd14a73cf4","tid":230751,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵免運幫手"},{"pid":"97a1095df5a217c46bcbc36f45f2f93bee0c8afc","tid":230751,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:02:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵免費幫手</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c8b0ea33c85f84e71c5eb1a7b9181f5f38b8e4d9","tid":230751,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"好坦白，除左玩財技，根本start up係唔需要商科人，除非佢真係好有料<br />\n<br />\n但你公司仔邊有錢玩財技，而醒目就唔會讀商科la"},{"pid":"5a0d7c9cb2ed7ea54a2d7f8c392ddc63591a7d4a","tid":230751,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:09:36.000Z","msg":"Sad but true<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"face8375f2cf20205808f0cec757abd8b7a28507","tid":230751,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike"